# Stay Safe Online – Prevention Checklist

##  General Safety Tips

* Do not click on unknown or suspicious links
* Always verify the sender before responding to emails or messages
* Use strong and unique passwords for all accounts
* Enable two-factor authentication (2FA) wherever possible
* Avoid sharing personal or sensitive information online
* Keep your devices and applications updated regularly
* Check for secure websites (https://) before entering any data
* Avoid downloading files or apps from untrusted sources

##  UPI / Financial Safety Tips

* Never share your OTP or UPI PIN with anyone
* Always verify payment requests before accepting or sending money

## Reporting Cybercrime

* National Cyber Crime Portal: https://cybercrime.gov.in
* Helpline Number: 1930
